      <p class="text-center" style="color: #6c757d;">To complete your registration, please use the OTP below:</p>
      <div class="text-center" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0;">OTP: <span style="color: #ee495e;">{{otp}}</span></div>
